"{\"uid\": \"thehollywoodgossip.com-2024-07-the-view-co-hosts-slam-critics-of-olympics-last-supper-drag-show\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByAuthorKay Rhodes  Published:Jul 30, 2024 at 3:22 PM \\u2022CategoryOlympics  Reading Time:3minutes  Candace Cameron Bure has gone from host ofThe Viewto Hot Topic.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 96, \"end\": 116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Candace Cameron Bure\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\"}, {\"begin\": 112, \"end\": 116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Bure\", \"score\": 0.980265051062511, \"rank\": 0.02013225801611749, \"text\": \"Bure\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Bure\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Bure\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the backlash from Cameron and Christian supporters against the 2024 ParisOlympicsopening ceremony, the hosts of the hit daytime talk show weigh in.\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 189, \"end\": 196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allison_Cameron\", \"score\": 0.9765220351242161, \"rank\": 0.024042432255837822, \"text\": \"Cameron\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allison_Cameron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allison_Cameron\"}, {\"begin\": 201, \"end\": 210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9972460980396806, \"rank\": 0.0025487740855154577, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Needless to say, they are not Team Candace.\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 363, \"entities\":