\"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Whoopi_Goldberg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Whoopi_Goldberg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are not trying to do anything except talk about the history.\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are showing you the history.\\\"\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 870, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In case you have not been following:Candace Cameron Burefelt the drag performance during the opening ceremony alluded to Leonardo da Vinci's iconic late 15th century painting depicting his interpretation of the Last Supper of Jesus Christ.\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 1111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 993, \"end\": 1010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2797314970480555e-21, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She called the performance \\\"disgusting.\\\"\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1152, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it has since been confirmed by organizers that the performance as in reference to a 17th century painting titled \\\"The Feast of the Gods\\\" by Dutch artist Jan van Bijlert, which depicts the Greek gods of Olympus crowded around a long table.\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1303, \"end\": 1308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.9920951236551435, \"rank\": 0.00796344404054067, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1316, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jan_van_Bijlert\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jan van Bijlert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jan_van_Bijlert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jan_van_Bijlert\"}, {\"begin\": 1351, \"end\": 1361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"score\": 0.988853663133258, \"rank\": 0.011271978132133618, \"text\": \"Greek gods\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\"}, {\"begin\": 1365, \"end\": 1372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\", \"score\": 0.9404438310675707, \"rank\": 0.06331917958113151, \"text\": \"Olympus\", \"types\": [\"Q8502\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, the damage had been done and people's minds - including Candace's - could not be swayed.\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1466, \"end\": 1473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"score\": 0.9999983509615004, \"rank\": 1.3764972604642493e-06, \"text\": \"Candace\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Which made Whoopi and co. that much angrier.\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1544, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than taking \\\"20 hours to write an email,\\\" the Oscar-winner suggested that individuals who were \\\"not happy\\\" with the vignette simply \\\"watch something else.\\\"\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1708, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just turn the TV off!\\\"\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whoopi exclaimed.\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1751, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Watch something else!\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Put the newspaper down, do not look at the pictures, these are choices.\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1846, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These are our choices.\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1869, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have the ability.\\\"\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1892, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Forget what Instagram is telling you,\\\" she went on.\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1907, \"end\": 1916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.234685383290804e-26, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you do not like it, go to something else!\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You do not have to stay!\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have it in your power to make the change.\\\"\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sara Haines, who often talks openly about her religion, agreed with Whoopi that the performance was not meant \\\"to be subversive, nor to mock or to shock,\\\" but rather \\\"to send a message of love, a message of inclusion and not at all to divide.\\\"\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2066, \"end\": 2077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sara_Haines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sara Haines\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sara_Haines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sara_Haines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I get so frustrated with religion,\\\" Sara admitted, before offering some advice to her fellow followers of faith.\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2348, \"end\": 2352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sara_Tancredi\", \"score\": 0.9995239031356867, \"rank\": 0.0004637222857981785, \"text\": \"Sara\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sara_Tancredi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sara_Tancredi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Do not go by the literal letter of the bible, go by the example of the word -- which is live with the grace, live with the forgiveness.\\\"\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ana Navarro then weighed in to point out that the Last Supper-evoking drag segment \\\"was a very small part\\\" of an event that was nearly four hours long.\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2564, \"end\": 2575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ana_Navarro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ana Navarro\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ana_Navarro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ana_Navarro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's what's consumed so much of America, I guess, and I would say, it happens every four years,\\\" Navarro said.\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2815, \"end\": 2822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jaime_Navarro\", \"score\": 0.9961503765545667, \"rank\": 0.003138594990613273, \"text\": \"Navarro\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jaime_Navarro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jaime_Navarro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There are young people who train their entire lives, to be there to represent our countries.\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2922, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Can we please give them the focus?\\\"\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2958, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, please - can we just watchSimone Bilesdominate please???\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 3021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Taylor Swift Responds to Horrific Stabbing at Event Inspired by Iconic Singer  Idiot Comedian Slams Taylor Swift, Says Travis Kelce is Totally Gonna Dump Her\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3023, \"end\": 3035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.049668090524709e-37, \"text\": \"Taylor Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\"}, {\"begin\": 3142, \"end\": 3154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Travis_Kelce\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Travis Kelce\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Travis_Kelce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Travis_Kelce\"}]}]}"